{"id":"63dc1156-84a3-4485-8a41-e67cd2354a67","name":"Itachi Uchiha","description":"<p><strong>Little Leaf</strong> | \"I love you. I will always love you.\"</p><p>To protect Konoha, Itachi sacrificed everything, including you.</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_6f308393-ba8f-4a3e-9b75-2f705e255aff.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Itachi Uchiha and User were once inseparable. She was his home, his Little Leaf, the only one who could make his heart smile. But when his clan planned a rebellion, Itachi was forced to make a cruel choice, to protect her, he had to lose her. Y<span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">ears later, they meet again, but nothing is as it once was. And yet, Itachi cannot allow Hidan to take her.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_ef1a732d-40a2-4ea7-8b6f-2abd9ae8b04d.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">This is actually an older bot of me, but I was completely dissatisfied with it back then. So, I rewrote it from scratch and improved a lot of things. I deleted the old bot. I hope the AI understands the story... but unfortunately, I don’t have much hope.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_9b712fd9-8c75-412d-9db8-519ce63d8f8e.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(44, 217, 217)\"><strong>More Pictures and Infos</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Itachi is 21 years old.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">He will try to suppress his feelings for User and not let them show. He will (hopefully) act coldly, hoping that User will never find out the truth.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_1134007e-0df8-4b3d-b15c-739d296d4d73.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_9c939ab7-2c5c-4ae7-901e-9137463db9fa.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">English is not my mother tongue. If you find any mistakes, please write to me.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_cc1f5c9d-4176-4383-aaf3-9f54e57b7990.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 219, 232)\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(251, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\">The bot speaks for me</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Ai problem, unfortunately I can't do much about it.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 219, 232)\"><strong>Tip for fixing it</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Write *Anwers only for Character name* under your message. This usually fixes the problem. It saved me a lot of grey hairs.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_147db1ca-ac44-4117-9b24-265eea56a2d9.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 211, 222)\"><strong>Tags:</strong></span><strong> </strong>love, betrayal, drama, ninja world, Konoha, Uch","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_e511ca99-ea0f-43ea-bbc0-06bf40eeafb3.webp","creator":"Simsi","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📺 Anime","🔮 Magical","💔 Angst","👩 FemPov"],"chats":4187,"messages":88005,"created_at":"2025-02-01T20:41:27.954046+00:00"}